DocumentComment: <text>Hand-curated SBOM for dicom-fuzzer 1.11.0. Lists direct
runtime dependencies declared in pyproject.toml plus two vendored components
that no scanner can see. Used as the "manual" side of sbom-overlay's dogfood
reconciliation fixture.</text>

